divs: Sighting DetailsMyself and 6 friends were at a park. I looked up to the sky and saw this neon green very bright object was moving across the sky at decent speed. I yelled wtf! The person sitting next to me glanced up in time to also see it before it just vanished or turned off its lights. No noise was heard but it was quite a good distance away.

Summary: Bright green object moving across the sky and then disappeared.
